# ============================================================================
# Reference material — re-cloneable / re-downloadable
# ============================================================================
# 4 reference prompt repos are tracked as git submodules (see .gitmodules).
# Submodule content takes ~400MB on disk locally but is NOT part of this repo
# — only the pinned commit references travel with `git push`.

# Arknights design analysis archive — keep only the design-system markdowns,
# skip the heavy PDF + art reference (~100 MB)
# arknights-analysis/arknights-art/
# arknights-analysis/UIUX-analysis-for-Arknights.pdf
# arknights-analysis/arknights-ui-ux-article/
# arknights-analysis/arknights-pdf-article/
# Note: arknights-analysis/arknights-design-system/ IS tracked (140 KB)
# — those are the four design-system docs DESIGN.md inherits from.

